Put your money where the support is ---
> 00:07.1 IDE interface: Intel Corporation 82371AB PIIX4 IDE (rev 01)
> 00: 86 80 11 71 05 00 80 02 01 80 01 01 00 40 00 00
> 40: 07 a3 70 c0 38 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00
This chipset is setup for PIO and DMA mode 2 for ATA-2.
There ULTRA DMA settings are not set and disabled!
This is why you are having problems........
